casebody.data:
David E. HILL, petitioner,
v.
Rudolph CONTRERAS, Judge, United States District Court for the District of Columbia. No. 15-6177. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 9, 2015.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States *489Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
